                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/961" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0172</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8303 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“消亡”还是“重生”？—盛天集团的战略变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Die or Live? The Strategic Change of Shengtian Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">焦豪，郭晋利</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">盛天集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有中小企业；战略变革；竞争优势</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Small &amp;amp; Medium State-owned Enterprise; Strategic change; Competitive advantage</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从1978年开始，我国进入经济体制转轨时期，即由计划经济向市场经济过渡的时期。在这一时期，国有企业是改革的重点。与大型国企有详细的变革指导战略不同，国有中小企业在这一进程中地位尴尬。一般而言，中小国有企业的变革以产权改革为主，企业具体的发展战略则涉及不多。但在复杂的环境中，为了获取更多的市场机会，战略变革成为中小国有企业发展过程中必须面对的问题。本案例描述了盛天集团在转轨背景下的发展历程，对其两次战略变革的过程进行了分析，总结出其实现战略变革的经验，即以产品为核心，通过制造环节的“一体化战略”建立企业的竞争优势，继而在产业链上进行拓展实现企业的“相关多元化”。在这个过程中需要较好地把握外部环境的变化、处理与利益相关者的关系以及提升自身能力。案例可以为能够对同样面临变革的其他中小国企提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since 1978, China&#39;s economic system gradually by the planning system to a market system changes, this process is called transition. During this period, the state-owned enterprise reform is a priority. Large state-owned development strategies have generally been developed by the state, small and medium state-owned enterprises are often ignored, and even become a victim of the policy. Faced with a complex environment, in order to obtain new opportunities, SMEs strategic change has become an inevitable choice. Shengtian Group as an example in this article, the author analyzes its strategic change process. The author believes, Shengtian Group moves the strategic change process is always based on its product. Manufacturing capacity expansion and technological innovation allows the company to achieve an integrated strategy. And then, by the extension of industrial chain, the company achieves the related diversification strategy. In the two processes, the company works well with the external environment, internal relations and its ability. The authors hope that this experience can provide some reference to other small and medium state-owned enterprises which also face the same situation. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理学》、《企业管理》、《公司战略》、《人力资源管理》、《管理咨询与诊断》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小企业战略变革过程</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
